      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00002",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "儿夫西凉未回转，倒叫宝钏挂心间。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00003",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "奴家，王宝钏。只因当年抛球招婿，打中薛郎。回转相府，与爹爹三击掌，誓死不回相府。不想薛郎降了红鬃烈马。圣上见喜，封为后军督府。我家爹爹上殿参奏一本，言道：西凉夏国，兴兵造反。命苏龙、魏虎挂帅。将我夫改为马前先行，前去征战西凉。至今十余载，音信全无。可怜我这几日身体有病。本当修书一封，寄与薛郎。山路遥远，不得传递。只怕我夫妻，今生就难以相见了！",
      "text_length": 172
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00004",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "雁仙自下场门暗上，站在大边椅上，连叫三声。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00005",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "且住！我想鸿雁乃是仁义之鸟，能与人传书寄柬。雁哪，雁哪！我有意修书一封，请你寄往西凉，寄与我夫平贵。你若愿去，与我把头三点！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00006",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "雁仙三点头，三叫。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00007",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀呀！它果然愿去。待奴修书。哎呀且住！寒窑之内，哪有文房四宝？这便怎么处？有了！我不免扯下罗裙，咬破中指，修写血书便了！",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00008",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "未曾修书心痛酸，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00009",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏咬左手指，用右手蘸血修书。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00010",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "喂呀呀……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00011",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "十指连心泪不干。上写宝钏修书柬：“拜上儿夫平贵男：妻为你懒把父母见，妻为你寒窑受熬煎。你若念在夫妻义，不分昼夜返长安。你若不念夫妻义，稳坐西凉莫回还。早来三天还相见，迟来三日不团圆！”修罢书信手发颤，",
      "text_length": 100
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00012",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "拴在宾鸿项下边。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00013",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "我不免将血书拴在鸿雁颈上便了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00014",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏拴血书。雁仙下。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00015",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "但愿宾鸿书寄到，免得奴家心内焦。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021008_e00016",
      "play_id": "03021008",
      "scene_id": "03021008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
